\\\\bigl(- a^3 \\\\delta M + a^2 \\\\delta a r + a \\\\delta M (2 M -  r) r + \
\\\\delta a r (-4 M^2 + 2 M r + r^2)\\\\bigr) + a \\\\bigl(6 M^2 \\\\delta a \
r (a^2 + 2 r^2) + (a^2 + r^2) (a^3 \\\\delta M - 2 a^2 \\\\delta a r - 3 \
\\\\delta a r^3) + 2 M \\\\delta a (a^4 - 2 a^2 r^2 - 3 r^4)\\\\bigr)}{6 GN \
\\\\pi a^2 (a^2 + r^2) \\\\bigl(a^2 + r (-2 M + r)\\\\bigr)}\"\>"], "Output",
